{
  "stem": "8212.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it slowly got again very upsetting, because we knew it's going to reach us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So it was a very unquiet time, not-- very perturbed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then, finally, the war came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The Maginot Line didn't hold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And again, we tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Everybody escaped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We took a train from Brussels.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We took, again, a little bit of luggage, whatever, and tried to go to Paris, where a brother of my mother had settled.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But we took this train, and we never arrived in Paris.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The train was bombarded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We stayed in that train for four days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And after stopping here and stopping there, we arrived somewhere in the south of France, in little-- in a little village.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It was a station with-- there was one station for three villages.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "One was His, Mane, and Touille.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we were-- we were taken to Touille, where we went to an old factory and we were put on straw.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We were just put up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And there, we stayed for a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we even tried-- there was a school, I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "My sister and I tried to go to the school, but the accent in-- the southern accent in France is so different from the other French that when we had dictation, we could hardly write it because the pronunciation was so different that it was very hard to follow.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And the way they had calcul, math, was like 50 years ago.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We were way ahead, so we didn't go back to that school, really.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It was ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we just lived on things that the peasants sold us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We made our own butter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We learned how to make butter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We bought cream.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We put it in a bottle, and we were shaking the bottle, and that's how we made our butter.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
